05:18.798 --> 05:21.621
people were telling you to do is what you did. You 
are responding to what the people will want. Do you

05:26.547 --> 05:33.594
see that through time as well, that your medicine 
has been reactive rather than... Yes, it's still

05:33.614 --> 05:36.797
reactive. Yeah. Rather than proactive. Even with 
the public health issue, which is something I

05:38.699 --> 05:44.605
would like to hear. Yeah. Do I think even in public 
health?

05:48.810 --> 05:48.910
Yeah. We're reactive. Does that bother you? Are 
you happy with that? No.

05:57.661 --> 05:57.721
No. And we have committee after committee trying 
to look down the future. But we're not good enough

06:02.767 --> 06:07.112
to see it correctly. And we react to what people 
then demand. And we do what people demand. If you

06:14.161 --> 06:17.545
don't do what people demand, you can go home. And

06:17.693 --> 06:40.825
veterinary medicine has changed because people 
have changed, not what we have done as a

06:17.693 --> 06:40.825
profession.

