really, you know, dogfights at one time. And then 
it eased off, and it got better and better, and I

11:44.631 --> 11:53.340
perceived that over the last several years that it 
The real problem had really gone away. Now, I'm

11:56.563 --> 12:05.456
sure there are instances out there where it still

11:56.563 --> 12:05.456
exists. Of course, the county agent and his staff 
are out there paid by somebody else to help the

12:05.476 --> 12:14.188
rural people. And they do a good job. And it's good 
