nearly all gone.

20:43.401 --> 20:49.388
What had been the major thrust or efforts of the 
TDMA, do you think? Well, I think it's just that. I

20:51.050 --> 20:53.053
think it's just that. Do what we, as a profession, 
we ought to perform as a profession. Each of us have

20:57.494 --> 21:07.350
an obligation to not just ourselves, to not just 
our little area, to not just our clients. We've got

21:07.370 --> 21:10.535
an obligation to our profession. Has there been 
any direct influence by TVMA, say, on policies of

21:10.555 --> 21:18.507
the College of Veterinary Medicine? Either 
deliberate or subconscious or... or whatever

21:21.434 --> 21:27.619
they wanted. In 1964,

21:27.639 --> 21:40.010
we decided here at the College of Veterinary 
Medicine to go on the trimester system. We were on

21:40.030 --> 21:43.133
the semester system for four years. And this was 
during the time of sparsity of veterinary

21:43.153 --> 21:51.340
practitioners.

21:57.209 --> 22:02.095
And it was perceived that we needed to produce more 
veterinarians. And this was not just Texas, this

22:03.616 --> 22:08.202
was a national position. And

22:08.222 --> 22:23.079
to get to that, you've got to do some things that 
will enhance that. And we studied it in the College

22:23.099 --> 22:26.423
of Veterinary Medicine. carefully over a period 
of a couple of years and decided that, you know, we

22:27.230 --> 22:37.967
could go three trimesters instead of two 
semesters. By doing some things, we can do as much

22:39.149 --> 22:43.996
in a trimester as we can do in a semester. A semester 
was a little bit longer than a trimester. But we did

22:47.262 --> 22:52.670
such things as all examinations were at 7 o'clock 
in the morning. That gave the whole rest of it. Full

22:54.922 --> 22:56.924
day activities. You can do things like that which 
put a little more burden on the student. But they

23:02.969 --> 23:07.753
can move and graduate in three years.

23:08.974 --> 23:14.059
We could better utilize our facilities that would 
go all the way through the summer. The semester

23:14.079 --> 23:21.485
system, you go nine months and you're off three 
months and come back in this clinic over here and

23:14.079 --> 23:21.485
these buildings sit here for three months. You 
know, what are you doing with them? We utilize that

23:23.947 --> 23:25.248
better. And the cost of the students is only three 
years instead of four years. Maybe the tuition is

23:35.497 --> 23:45.386
about the same as the four year, but the living cost 
